{
  "commands": [
    "Get-BGFirewallRules -Type Enabled -AllProperties -ReturnObject | Export-Clixml -Path $(\"{0}\\Windows\\Temp\\BGFirewallRules_{1}.bak\" -f $env:SystemDrive, $(Get-Date -Format yyyyMMdd_hh.mm.ss.tt.zz))",
    "Get-BGFirewallRules -Type Enabled -AllProperties -ReturnObject | Export-Clixml -Path $(\"{0}\\Windows\\Temp\\BGFirewallRules_Last.bak\" -f $env:SystemDrive) -Force",
    "Get-BGFirewallRules -Type Enabled -AllProperties",
    "Disable-BGAllFirewallRules -Force",
    "Add-BGFirewallRule -RuleName $(Get-ChildItem -Path $(\"{0}\\Tools\\FireWallRules\\*.Rule\" -f $BluGenieModulePath) | Select-Object -ExpandProperty Fullname)",
    "Set-BGFirewallStatus -ProfileType DOMAIN+PRIVATE+PUBLIC -Outbound Block -Inbound Allow",
    "Set-BGFirewallGPOStatus -ServiceState Remove",
    "Set-BGRemoteDesktopProcess -Value Enable",
    "Update-BGFirewallProfileStatus -ProfileType DOMAIN+PRIVATE+PUBLIC -Status ENABLE"
  ],
  "systems": [
    "$exec.event.host"
  ]
}
